cal seminary she also attended the north texas school of midwifery and served as a certified professional midwife in the dallasft worth area providing nutritional counseling prenatal and postpartum care and newborn assessments as she attended her clients with home births creation therapy is the foundation of counseling at lionsgate the temperament analysis profile identifies the temperament needs in a counselee and helps them find balance in order to relieve inner stress creation therapy is based on the theory of temperament and focuses on the uniqueness of each individual and thereby opens the door to finding peace within themselves within their environment and with the lord that created them by understanding their individual temperament understanding the inner man counselees gain the knowledge to better understand themselves their strengths as well as their weaknesses according to the national christian counselor’s association this therapeutic model has a proven success rate of  this percentile is based on therapy conducted with over  counselees rainer maria rilke the thcentury german poet wrote to a young wouldbe poet to “live from a deep place” only then rilke said would his writing become great as a life coach dottie supports clients to find their deep place by discovering their life purpose mission and vision individuals as well as businesses are turning to life coaching as a means of steering their lives to live by “true north” as they align their life and work with their core values dottie has traveled throughout the united states as a conference speaker and teacher on subjects as “the art of hearing god” and “how god speaks in dreams and visions” she has trained and mentored hundreds of people in the ability to understand the meaning of their dreams for more information about future classes scheduled in the chattanooga area or to make an appointment for counseling or life coaching please contact dottie at dottiestewartyahoocom  or call  her office is locate