uel johnson john locke isaac newton thomas reid adam smith mary wollstonecraft united states benjamin franklin thomas jefferson james madison george mason thomas paine v t e classical economists francis hutcheson bernard mandeville david hume adam smith jeanbaptiste say thomas malthus james mill francis place david ricardo henry thornton john ramsay mcculloch james maitland th earl of lauderdale jeremy bentham jean charles léonard de sismondi johann heinrich von thünen john stuart mill henry charles carey nassau william senior edward gibbon wakefield john rae frédéric bastiat thomas tooke robert torrens authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc x bnf cb data ulan  nla  ndl  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlefrancishutchesonphilosopheroldid categories  births deathspeople from saintfieldulster scots peoplethcentury irish writersthcentury philosophersirish philosophersalumni of the university of glasgowacademics of the university of glasgowconsequentialistsearly modern philosophersempiricistsenlightenment philosophershumor researchersministers of the church of scotlandscottish scholars and academicspeople of the scottish enlightenmentirish presbyteriansburials at st marys churchyard dublinhidden categories pages with citations lacking titlesuse dmy dates from march articles needing additional references from february all articles needing additional referencesarticles with hcardsall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from february wikipedia articles incorporating a citation from the  encyclopaedia britannica with wikisource referencewikipedia articles incorporating text from the  encyclopædia britannicaarticles with project gutenberg linksarticles containing frenchlanguage textarticles containing hebrewlanguage textarticles containing latinlanguage textwikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with